cxro.common.io.modbus.client

Class ReadRODiscretesTransaction

  • java.lang.Object
    • cxro.common.io.modbus.client.ModbusTransaction
      • cxro.common.io.modbus.client.ReadRODiscretesTransaction

  • public final class ReadRODiscretesTransaction
extends ModbusTransaction
    Class implementing a ReadRODiscretes transaction. The implementation directly correlates with the modbus function read discrete inputs (FC 2). It encapsulates the corresponding request and response messages.

    Discrete inputs are readonly signals
